(2315, 1, '2017-10-23 20:10:04', '2017-10-23 20:10:04', '<h3><span style="color: #3366ff;">SERVICE</span></h3>\r\n<h5>Request an appointment by logging in to our <a href="https://www.europeansautotech.com/">Service Facility website</a></h5>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPassport Motors Service Center Page Content: http://www.passportmotors.com/web/service\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nExtending the lifespan of your vehicle involves having an in auto repair center Dallas that you can trust. When it comes to luxury vehicles, this is truer than ever before. Caring for a luxury automobile requires someone who is familiar with high-end cars, with the expertise to care for them with the treatment that they need. Passport Motors has been caring for luxury cars for over 15 years, with a proven reputation as one of Dallas best luxury car repair centers.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWith any vehicle, it is important to keep up with a basic maintenance schedule. This includes things such as oil changes, brake inspections, replacing of air filter or fuel filter, and the checking and changing of belts. Preventative maintenance is the best kind of car maintenance, as it keeps the car running smoothly and prevents major problems before they crop up.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAt Passport Motors, we can help you maintain your vehicle to keep it running well. Contact us today to schedule a tune-up to make sure everything is working properly inside your vehicle.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAt our luxury car service center in Plano, TX, we also specialize in mechanical repairs for your vehicle. This could include repair work on your transmission, steering and suspension, or even electronic work in the diagnostics of your vehicle. If the worst happens and you need a full engine repair or complete drive train repair on your luxury vehicle, we are here to help with our team of highly-trained mechanics.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAt times, repairs might not be blatantly obvious, but they could still be very necessary to make sure the vehicle is safe out on the road. For example, if your brakes are seeing significant wear and tear, you may not even know it until you run into a problem on the road. Passport Motors can help you inspect that and either give your car a clean bill of health, or suggest and perform any repairs that are needed.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIn some cases, we can determine if your vehicle has structural damage or if strictly cosmetic repairs are needed. Cosmetic damage could be something as small as a rock chip to bumper damage or panel dents. We can assess what type of work is needed, and then perform the repairs, no matter if they are structural or cosmetic.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWhen it comes to your luxury car, you need a professional service center with experience handling top of the line vehicles. At Passport Motors, that is our specialty. With excellent customer service, our main priority is getting you the best possible service at an affordable price. Give us a call at 972-422-9941 or stop by at 3953 N. Central Expwy Plano, 75023.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLet us show you why we are a premier luxury car repair center in Dallas!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Service', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'service', '', '', '2017-10-23 20:36:49', '2017-10-23 20:36:49', '', 0, 'http://passport.autocomp.us/?page_id=2315', 0, 'page', '', 0),
